eExam.15
Type:
ExtremityAssessmentLocation, simple content
eExam.15 Extremity Assessment Finding Location No No The location of the patient's extremity assessment findings. Optional Element eExam.16 - Extremities Assessment represents Version 2.2.1 NHTSA Injury Matrix elements E15_08 Upper Extremities and E15_10 Lower Extremities AND E16_17 Extremities-Right Upper Assessment, E16_18 Extremities-Right Lower Assessment, E16_19 Extremities-Left Upper Assessment, and E16_20 Extremities-Left Lower Assessment. The element value choices have been combined and expanded.

The element value choices have been combined and expanded.
